<div id="quick-start" class="mb-20">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8 text-center">Quick Start</h2>

    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="bg-zinc-900 border border-zinc-800 rounded-lg p-6">
            <div class="font-mono text-sm space-y-6">
                <div>
                    <div class="text-zinc-400 text-xs mb-2">
                        1. Deploy your worker (one click)
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-zinc-950 rounded p-3 text-zinc-300">
                        <a
                            href="https://deploy.workers.cloudflare.com"
                            target="_blank"
                            rel="noopener noreferrer"
                            class="text-amber-400 hover:underline"
                        >
                            deploy.workers.cloudflare.com
                        </a>
                        <span class="text-zinc-500"> (sets up R2 + D1 + generates a token)</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div>
                    <div class="text-zinc-400 text-xs mb-2">
                        2. Install the CLI
                    </div>
                    <pre class="bg-zinc-950 rounded p-3 overflow-x-auto text-zinc-300"><code>npm install -g residue</code></pre>
                </div>

                <div>
                    <div class="text-zinc-400 text-xs mb-2">
                        3. Login with your worker URL and token
                    </div>
                    <pre class="bg-zinc-950 rounded p-3 overflow-x-auto text-zinc-300"><code>residue login</code></pre>
                </div>

                <div>
                    <div class="text-zinc-400 text-xs mb-2">
                        4. Initialize in your repo
                    </div>
                    <pre class="bg-zinc-950 rounded p-3 overflow-x-auto text-zinc-300"><code>cd your-project
residue init</code></pre>
                    <p class="text-zinc-500 text-xs mt-2">
                        Installs git hooks and detects available agent adapters.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="text-zinc-500 text-xs mt-4 pt-4 border-t border-zinc-800">
                    That's it. Commit and push as usual. Conversations are captured automatically.
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
